Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.04,0:00:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  我們來決定一下本班的出展項目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.96,0:00:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰有什麼主意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.25,0:00:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我想演戲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.19,0:00:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼屋之類的也不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.06,0:00:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可麗餅店
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.43,0:00:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話就普通點搞個燒烤店之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.66,0:00:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  老師  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.65,0:00:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師覺得「心跳！帥哥多多的露天啤酒店」不錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.90,0:00:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師請閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.99,0:00:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕君好冷漠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前還說長大了要當由香里姐姐的老公
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.82,0:00:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨佔那南國水果一般的豐滿身材…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.94,0:00:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可麗餅店和燒烤店
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.82,0:00:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  Cosplay咖啡店如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.89,0:00:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cosplay咖啡…咦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cosplay咖啡店就是Cosplay後的店員來接客的咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.79,0:00:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正菜單裡有可麗餅和燒烤也沒什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.94,0:01:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又可以像鬼屋一樣做各種裝扮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還可以像演戲一般扮演各種角色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.86,0:01:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶  不覺得很贊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.73,0:01:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  為什麼隔壁班的你會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.04,0:01:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  這些小事情就不要在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.28,0:01:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何嘛  Cosplay咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是像在秋葉原流行的女僕咖啡店之類的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.91,0:01:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能穿可愛的衣服倒是不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.40,0:01:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生要幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.63,0:01:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  要是讓女生穿的話我推薦學校泳裝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.26,0:01:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不認同舊學校泳裝之外的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.54,0:01:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  樸素的水手服也會讓人耳目一新
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.48,0:01:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那麼就讓我們投票決定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如各位所見  出展項目決定為Cosplay咖啡店了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.78,0:01:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起開心地辦好Cosplay咖啡店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.66,0:01:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來出展項目也決定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.52,0:01:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,執行委員  加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班裡的出展項目決定好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是到頭來還是採用了信長的主意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  要是那麼想搞Cosplay咖啡店的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.17,0:03:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在自己的班裡搞不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.69,0:03:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在班裡也提過了的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.97,0:03:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過以小差距輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.18,0:03:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想在裕人的班裡復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.85,0:04:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這會叫復仇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cosplay咖啡店不是很有趣的樣子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好  能穿上什麼衣服呢  好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  雖然決定是Cosplay咖啡店了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.85,0:04:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我也不太懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本想著是像秋葉原的女僕咖啡店一般的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信長卻說不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我根本就不太懂Cosplay和咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人  那個…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人裕人  執行委員要到會議室集合了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.83,0:04:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉春香  之後再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點快點  乃木坂同學  對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.85,0:04:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃木坂前輩今年也參加白鳳祭的選美嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.09,0:05:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩要是參加的話  就一定是二連霸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.39,0:05:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃木坂前輩  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥當執行委員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  雖然看起來很辛苦的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過他很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是既然如此的話  要是姐姐是搭檔就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油做好執行委員
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人的距離閃電拉近之類的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.77,0:05:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千載難逢的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.42,0:05:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  我們自言自語
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:06:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那姐姐就是在背後支持著大哥哥  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我想如果能稍微幫上他的忙的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是一樣賢淑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是還很天真哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須得更積極地追求大哥哥才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積極地？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  第一次「大哥哥的心捕獲大作戰」會議現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.10,0:06:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做便當帶去也很好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.89,0:06:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給他送親手做的餅乾和紅茶套餐之類的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆綁架了他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月  好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.17,0:06:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用餅乾去綁架？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:07:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他還有問他「累了嗎  裕人」之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫  幫  幫他按摩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夏小姐太大膽了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.97,0:07:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太色了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這  這樣的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在白鳳祭的最後一起跳土風舞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土風舞…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  裕  裕人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨君嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才和椎菜一起出去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像說有什麼執行委員會之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.17,0:07:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:07:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟我來一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  春香知不知道哪有賣Cosplay衣服的店子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想見識一下實物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡店的裝潢和菜單倒是都基本想好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是關於Cosplay就完全著不了手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.44,0:08:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在夏漫展的時候春香似乎又對Cosplay很有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想春香的話或許會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.33,0:08:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次跟裕人去秋葉原的時候見到過了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地址我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那這週的星期天能帶我去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.28,0:08:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的  這週星期天對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.14,0:08:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期天…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.97,0:08:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  這週星期天對吧  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了  這樣的話Cosplay咖啡店也總算能弄妥了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭候您的光臨  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人還是那麼多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙休日人特別多  請注意不要走散哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  你好像特別開心的樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.67,0:09:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害  這些全是Cosplay的衣服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.44,0:09:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裡也接受訂做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這只是一小部分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜想曲女子學院長曲棍球部的冬裝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.79,0:09:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有笨拙女孩小秋的魔法服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪個都好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個太輕飄飄的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.69,0:09:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是用來接客的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}是否方便活動呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.79,0:10:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  對了  今天是為了看Cosplay咖啡店的服裝來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人  服裝是由班裡的大家來做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我想在這裡看看實物來參考
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒有給每人都買一套的預算
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.04,0:10:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話  這件如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法大餐的夏服版
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.51,0:10:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製作方法簡單  而且又方便活動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.90,0:10:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件是笨拙女孩小秋的天使版
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製作方法似乎太複雜了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的哦  做工意外地簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不挑身材  大家應該都能穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  果然還是女孩子比較瞭解這些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪  哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香也想穿穿這件嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  一定很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:10:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有興趣的話  可以試穿一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試  試穿？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中意的話  不妨就試穿一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…那個…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.76,0:11:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先試穿一下看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…呃…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.59,0:11:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想試穿一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  請到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  那個…請稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:12:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  裕人…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  去買了參考資料…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個  怎…怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕…裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個  非常適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.35,0:12:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就像真正的天使一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.67,0:12:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.24,0:12:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午好  店長在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.43,0:12:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕…裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.85,0:12:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  緊急事態
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨  朝倉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  店長上次和你談起的小皮羅的插肩袖的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}是的  姑且是做出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好擠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:12:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.59,0:12:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}哦  還不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  在信長回去之前請忍耐下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春…春香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.80,0:13:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕…人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}那麼  這件事就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.45,0:13:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}再見咯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}歡迎再次光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.43,0:13:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總  總之學到了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  不用這麼客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微幫上你的忙了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.59,0:13:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是一點點  幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.89,0:13:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  這個送你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.08,0:13:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.28,0:13:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這  這是笨拙女孩小秋的八音盒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.76,0:13:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛看到的  作為今天的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.11,0:14:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮  禮物什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不過是把你帶到店裡而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這回事  你幫了大忙了  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.51,0:14:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  美…美夏？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}性感的美夏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候記下號碼的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.31,0:14:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥  姐姐在你那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.14,0:14:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你現在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個  快帶著姐姐離開那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.27,0:14:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親往你們那裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.48,0:14:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄冬先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.43,0:14:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在剛才帶著HELL  HOUND出擊了  不快點逃跑的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說  為什麼要逃跑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐今天和父親約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.39,0:14:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是一個名叫波里尼的著名鋼琴大師要見她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.13,0:14:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來定在今天  父親也很期待著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.18,0:14:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…莫非
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:15:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐放了父親鴿子  選擇和大哥哥一起約會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.14,0:15:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是被父親發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.49,0:15:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我找到了  果然和你這傢伙在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.47,0:15:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄冬先生  春香她沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.06,0:15:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯的是強逼她約會的我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.91,0:15:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己承認自己的惡行  好膽量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我咬緊牙關
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.93,0:15:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.87,0:15:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.08,0:15:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.71,0:15:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們  打算幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:15:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的請求  親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.67,0:16:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都是這樣一時頭腦發熱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.01,0:16:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先聽聽他們倆怎麼說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好聽的  全都是那個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你先閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了春香  讓我聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼擅自放棄了和波里尼老師的會面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.74,0:16:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前和你說好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.61,0:16:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓我們承認你的興趣  就要好好的學習
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.36,0:16:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次這樣該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開心？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  因為是裕人第一次拜託我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到能幫上裕人的忙  我就很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:17:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我知道放棄和父親的約定很不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.46,0:17:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  今天對我來說是很重要的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.24,0:17:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何我都想幫助裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  錯的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有考慮到春香是否有空  硬是拜託她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.81,0:17:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我是以自己的意願選擇了和裕人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.94,0:17:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  就算是這樣  也是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況大致上瞭解了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有兩人互相重視對方的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.19,0:17:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這次的事給波里尼老師和父親添了麻煩是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也違反了和我所做的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.99,0:17:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.82,0:17:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  應該不會再發生同樣的事情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:17:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  這次就看在兩人之間感情的份上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:18:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破例不予以追究了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.69,0:18:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋穗小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  姐姐  大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能圓滿收場  比什麼都好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.30,0:18:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  又給裕人添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.91,0:18:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的是沒用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了  這話就不要說了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  不是沒用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了春香  我才能確定Cosplay咖啡店的服裝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是不考慮你的安排  一味地依靠你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.45,0:18:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為這次的道歉  或者說道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次有什麼我能幫的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.29,0:18:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  那個…道謝的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都送了我這個八音盒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這個無關
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都行哦  不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.37,0:18:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.84,0:19:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.51,0:19:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土風舞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.48,0:19:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白…白鳳祭最後的土風舞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能和我一起跳的話我會很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.29,0:19:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我想和裕人一起跳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者說如果不是裕人的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.38,0:19:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是裕人的話  我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  如果我可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的嗎  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.38,0:19:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  哎呀  年輕真好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.21,0:19:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不能錯過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攝像準備
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  有這麼多資料的話  服裝就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.45,0:19:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是乃木坂同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:20:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於時裝也很在行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  這樣無論如何也要讓Cosplay咖啡店辦成功
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢噢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是乃木坂同學  好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.67,0:21:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人  請加油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.57,0:21:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.03,0:21:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵～  給大哥哥的慰勞品嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.61,0:21:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.09,0:21:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天白鳳祭就正式開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天會忙到比較晚的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.89,0:21:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～  原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.87,0:21:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親手製作的餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.69,0:21:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.83,0:21:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.63,0:22:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人  還在的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.28,0:22:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.72,0:22:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.65,0:22:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.84,0:22:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃木坂同學
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.67,0:24:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「停滯」著的春香小姐  想要打開「永恆之門」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.94,0:24:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  姐姐不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.85,0:24:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有歡樂和悲傷的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.93,0:24:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.02,0:24:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香小姐停止了時間
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.00,0:24:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.41,0:24:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.39,0:24:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「想要、在一起…」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.46,0:24:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要記得看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.22,0:24:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最優先事項
